---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lang = 'en' as const;
---
<Layout title="SAP Roll-Out & Localization" lang={lang}>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-24 bg-surface-container overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto px-12 md:px-24">
            <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">SAP ROLL-OUT & LOCALIZATION</span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold font-headline text-on-background tracking-tight mb-8">SAP Roll-Out & Localization Services</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">Expand your global SAP landscape with speed, control, and full compliance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What is Roll-Out -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">What is SAP Roll-Out?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6">SAP Roll-Out is not a greenfield implementation. It is the structured expansion of an existing SAP system into new countries, business units, or operational entities.</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">The foundation of this process is the <strong class="text-on-background">global SAP template</strong>, which ensures consistency while enabling controlled scalability across the organization.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Standardization & Flexibility -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-on-background text-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">Balancing Standardization and Flexibility</h2>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">A successful roll-out requires maintaining global standards while adapting to local realities. This ensures both governance and agility.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">verified</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface">Existing SAP design is preserved</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">compare</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface">Fit/Gap analysis identifies required adjustments</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">tune</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface">Local requirements are integrated in a controlled manner</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">shield</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface">Expansion is achieved without disrupting the core system</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Localization -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">LOCALIZATION</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">Localization for Türkiye and Global Markets</h2>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-4">Localization is a critical component of any roll-out project, especially in markets with complex regulatory environments.</p>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm">All requirements are embedded into SAP in a standardized, auditable, and scalable structure while preserving the global template.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">gavel</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Tax & Accounting</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Compliance with local tax and accounting regulations</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">receipt_long</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">e-Transformation</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">e-Invoice, e-Archive, e-Delivery, e-Ledger</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">assessment</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Statutory Reporting</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Reporting and declaration obligations</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">hub</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Gov Integrations</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Government-compliant integrations</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Inbound / Outbound -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto px-12 md:px-24">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-primary group-hover:text-white">flight_land</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Companies Entering Turkey</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We seamlessly integrate your global SAP standards into Turkey's complex and dynamic regulatory environment. From full Revenue Administration (GİB) compliance and <a href="/en/services" class="text-primary hover:text-plum transition-colors font-medium underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4">mandatory e-Transformation</a> packages to specialized requirements like <a href="/en/rollout" class="text-primary hover:text-plum transition-colors font-medium underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4">TMS 29 Inflation Accounting</a>, we architect every step without disrupting your central system template. <br/><br/><strong class="text-primary font-medium">Bank Integration Assurance:</strong> Going beyond regulatory compliance, we also deliver complex <a href="/en/sap-cash-management" class="text-primary hover:text-plum transition-colors font-medium underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4">Online Direct Debit System (DBS)</a> networks and multi-bank integration processes right at the core of your ERP roll-out.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-primary group-hover:text-white">flight_takeoff</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Companies Expanding Abroad</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We bring cross-border operational capability and agility to your Turkey-based central SAP architecture. While adapting to the local legal frameworks (<strong class="text-primary font-medium">e.g., Peppol Invoicing</strong>, tax authority declarations) of diverse ecosystems across Europe, MENA, and Turkic Republics, we provide your enterprise with consolidated reporting capabilities under international <a href="/en/consulting" class="text-primary hover:text-plum transition-colors font-medium underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4">IFRS and Multi-GAAP standards</a>. We build a transparent financial foundation that eliminates technical boundaries for your <a href="/en/contact" class="text-primary hover:text-plum transition-colors font-medium underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4">global operations</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Typical Use Cases -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-primary text-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Typical Use Cases</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">public</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Expanding operations into a new country</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">corporate_fare</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Integrating subsidiaries into a central SAP system</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">factory</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Connecting new plants, warehouses, or logistics centers</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">merge</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Aligning acquired companies with the existing template</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">upgrade</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Gradual transformation of legacy systems into modern SAP</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                    <p class="text-center font-bold text-sm">One system, one data model,<br/>centralized control.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- End-to-End Methodology -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">End-to-End Roll-Out Methodology</h2>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant">A structured approach ensures predictable and successful outcomes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">1</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Template Design</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">2</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Localization</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">3</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Integration & Data</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">4</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Fit/Gap Workshop</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">5</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Testing & QA</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">6</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Cutover</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">7</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Hypercare</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Benefits -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Key Benefits</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">public</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Standardization across multi-country operations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">gavel</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Full compliance with local regulations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">savings</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Reduced integration and development costs</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">visibility</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Enhanced global reporting and financial visibility</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">share</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Reusable improvements across the organization</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">trending_up</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Scalable SAP investments with lower incremental cost</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="bg-on-background rounded-md p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline text-white mb-6">Let's Define Your Roll-out & Localization Needs</h2>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8">Expand your global SAP landscape with speed, control, and full compliance.</p>
                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <a href="/en/contact" class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-bold hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors shadow-lg">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
